@NODE WI_WHAT "What is it?"

    What is it?

    My holiday pictures had been lying around for quite some time and I never
    really got to buying photoalbums. So I decided to scan then and keep my
    photoalbum on a CD as a set of HTML files.

    I didn't feel like coding every HTML page by hand so Photoalbum Creator was
    born.

    Photoalbum Creator is a set of databasefiles, a form and some DML programs 
    intended to be used with Superbase Professional. If used correctly it will 
    generate a complete web-site with your pictures and comment. An example 
    database and website is included to give you an initial impression af what
    Photalbum Creator can do.

    You can find a demo version of @{"Superbase Professional" link WI_NEED} on Aminet in the directory biz/dbase. This demo 
    is limited to a maximum of 35 records, but that will do as an introduction 
    to PhotoalbumCreator. 
    There was also a full version of Superbase Professional on CUCD22, the cover CD of CU Amiga 22. 
    Alternatively you can buy the latest version of Superbase Professional Amiga from Mr. Hardware Computers. 

    Feel free to contact @{"me" link WI_WHO} with any comments or questions.

  
@ENDNODE

