@NODE WI_NEED "What do you need?"

    What do you need?

    All you need is a full version or a demo of Superbase Professional and a
    browser.

    - The demo version which is limited to databases of maximum 35 records can be
      found on Aminet in biz/dbase.
    - Some time ago a full version of Superbase Professional was released on the
      covercd of CU Amiga 22.
    - You can still get Superbase Professional as a commercial package from
      Mr. Hardware Computers.

    - Any browser will do. I tested the generated code with IBrowse 2.2 and 2.3, but since
      nothing fancy is generated, I suppose any browser will do.
                
@ENDNODE

@NODE WI_INST "How to install it?"

    How to install it?

    Create a directory anywhere on your harddisk and unpack the archive there.
    An installer script will be added later.
                
@ENDNODE

@NODE WI_HOW "How to use it?"

    How to use it?

    Start Superbase and open the form 'Photoalbum'.
    More instructions will be added later.
                
@ENDNODE

